msgctxt "an3.30:2.6"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, purisassa ucchaṅge nānākhajjakāni ākiṇṇāni—"
msgstr ""
"It’s like a person who has different kinds of food crammed on their lap—"

msgctxt "an3.30:2.7"
msgid "tilā taṇḍulā modakā badarā."
msgstr "such as sesame, rice, sweets, or jujube—"

msgctxt "an3.30:2.8"
msgid "So tamhā āsanā vuṭṭhahanto satisammosā pakireyya."
msgstr ""
"so that if they get up from the seat without mindfulness, everything gets "
"scattered."

